254: /*MC
255:   DMInterpolationInfo - Structure for holding information about interpolation on a mesh

257:   Level: intermediate

259:   Synopsis:
260:     comm   - The communicator
261:     dim    - The spatial dimension of points
262:     nInput - The number of input points
263:     points - The input point coordinates
264:     cells  - The cell containing each point
265:     n      - The number of local points
266:     coords - The point coordinates
267:     dof    - The number of components to interpolate

269: .seealso: DMInterpolationCreate(), DMInterpolationEvaluate(), DMInterpolationAddPoints()
270: M*/
271: struct _DMInterpolationInfo {
272:   MPI_Comm   comm;
273:   PetscInt   dim;    /*1 The spatial dimension of points */
274:   PetscInt   nInput; /* The number of input points */
275:   PetscReal *points; /* The input point coordinates */
276:   PetscInt  *cells;  /* The cell containing each point */
277:   PetscInt   n;      /* The number of local points */
278:   Vec        coords; /* The point coordinates */
279:   PetscInt   dof;    /* The number of components to interpolate */
280: };
281: typedef struct _DMInterpolationInfo *DMInterpolationInfo;
